#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>version</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>version</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:651
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>version</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>version</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid "Return &ktimetracker;'s version."
msgstr "Retourne la version de &ktimetracker;."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:655
#, no-c-format
msgid "QString version()"
msgstr "QString version()"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:658 index.docbook:677 index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Description"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>version()</function> is a &DBus; call that returns "
"&ktimetracker;'s version number; for example 4.3.1. The version number is "
"returned as a string in the typical &GNU; format of major.minor.bugfix."
msgstr ""
"<function>version()</function> est un appel &DBus; qui retourne la version "
"de &ktimetracker;, par exemple 4.3.1. La version est retournée sous forme de "
"chaine de caractères, dont le format majeure.mineure.correction est "
"caractéristique de &GNU;."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>quit</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>quit</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:670
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>quit</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>quit</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit &ktimetracker;'."
msgstr "Quitter &ktimetracker;."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid "QString quit()"
msgstr "QString quit()"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>quit()</function> is a &DBus; call that provides a way that an "
"external program can gracefully shutdown &ktimetracker;."
msgstr ""
"<function>quit()</function> est un appel &DBus; qui permet à un programme "
"externe de terminer élégamment &ktimetracker;."

#. Tag: refentrytitle
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refentrytitle>addTask</refentrytitle>"
msgstr "<refentrytitle>addTask</refentrytitle>"

#. Tag: refname
#: index.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid "<refname>addTask</refname>"
msgstr "<refname>addTask</refname>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: index.docbook:725
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add new task."
msgstr "Ajoute une nouvelle activité."

#. Tag: synopsis
#: index.docbook:728
#, no-c-format
msgid "QString addTask(QString taskname)"
msgstr "QString addTask(QString nom-tâche)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "Paramètres"

#. Tag: parameter
#: index.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid "taskname"
msgstr "nom-tâche"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:735
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of new task."
msgstr "Le nom d'une activité."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:744
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<function>addTask(QString taskname)</function> is a &DBus; call that adds a "
"new top-level to-do to the current storage. The UID of the new task is "
"returned."
msgstr ""
"<function>addTask(QString nom-tâche)</function> est un appel &DBus; ajoutant "
"une nouvelle tâche au niveau le plus haut dans l'enregistrement actuel. "
"Cette fonction retourne l'identifiant « UID » de la nouvelle tâche."

